                            </p>

                            <hr>

                            <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary rounded-pill w-100">
                                Apply Now
                            </a>

                        </div>

                    </div>

                </div>


                <div class="col-lg-4">

                    <div class="card border-0 shadow-lg h-100">

                        <div class="card-body">

                            <div class="d-flex justify-content-between">

                                <h5 class="fw-bold">
                                  DBA
